ef=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lgk1665702671677.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lgk1665702671677.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lgk1665702671677.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lgk1665702671677\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the time, in seconds, that the splash screen logo is displayed. This setting\n    applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface IDE.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lgk1665702671677__topic_d144476e1_d144477e1_d144478e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lgk1665702671677__p_d144479e1_d144480e1_d144481e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">LogoTime</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Seconds</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">OFF</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lgk1665702671677__section_gxm_mkc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d252887e71\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"lgk1665702671677__ul_blj_nkc_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lgk1665702671677__li_d50381e1_d50382e1_d50383e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Seconds</var>—alowed values are <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> through\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">60</code>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lgk1665702671677__li_d50384e1_d50385e1_d50386e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">OFF</code>—logo is switched off completely </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lgk1665702671677__li_d50387e1_d50388e1_d50389e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—a small window is displayed while Uniface is loading. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"lgk1665702671677__table_w2849ab1b5b3b5_w2850ab1b5b3_w2851ab1b5_w2852ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">3</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> File section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ila1665702671184.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ila1665702671184.html\" title=\"The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application.\">[application]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lco1665702671609.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Logo</a><p>Specifies the name of an image file to be used as the application splash screen logo. This setting applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface IDE.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529557\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529557\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "LogoTime Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the time, in seconds, that the splash screen logo is displayed. This setting applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface IDE. LogoTime = Seconds | OFF | 0 Arguments Seconds —alowed values are 0 through 60 . OFF —logo is switched off completely 0 —a small window is displayed while Uniface is loading. Default value: 3 File section: [application] Related Links Logo Specifies the name of an image file to be used as the application splash screen logo. This setting applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface IDE. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}